m individual medley title\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 847}, {\"ngram\": \"his billing\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 875}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He becomes just the fourth swimmer to win two individual titles in a single day and the first since 1976 after being cheered on at a cacophonous La Defense Arena.\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 1073, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just the fourth swimmer\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 945}, {\"ngram\": \"two individual titles\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 974}, {\"ngram\": \"a single day\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 990}, {\"ngram\": \"a cacophonous La Defense Arena\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1072}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marchand had to do it the hard way, too.\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1115, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Marchand\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1083}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the butterfly, he went head-to-head with defending champion and world record holder Kristof Milak but edged out the Hungarian by 0.54 seconds.\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1261, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1211, \"end\": 1216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milak_Assembly_constituency\", \"score\": 0.5830357787753622, \"rank\": 0.7151603246735387, \"text\": \"Milak\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milak_Assembly_constituency\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milak_Assembly_constituency\"}, {\"begin\": 1235, \"end\": 1244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.9999286588839781, \"rank\": 7.065554670581561e-05, \"text\": \"Hungarian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the butterfly\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1132}, {\"ngram\": \"head\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1154}, {\"ngram\": \"0.54 seconds\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1260}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zac Stubblety-Cook was the Tokyo 2020 gold medallist in the breaststroke but, despite hi